latestPosts.caption:
Hey Loves, allow me to introduce myself 💛!

My name is Rinali, but you can call me Rin! I was born and raised in South Africa 🇿🇦 and moved to the US when I was 9. I’m an April Aries, and I love the beach and margaritas. 🍹 

Married and a proud girl mom of three beautiful girls. 💕 

With 12+years of experience, I specialize in haircoloring—balayage, lived-in colors, and precision haircuts—Pixie cuts and Bobs. ✂️ 

I would love to be your forever hairstylist and make your hair dreams a reality. 🫶🏻

Comment and tell me something about yourself!
